{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/198/comments/47603014.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/issues/198#comment-47603014"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/198.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 198, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}ts=1606789"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "sdformat", "full_name": "osrf/sdformat", "uuid": "{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}"}, "title": "sdformat install not relocatable: sdf::findFile searches original install location"}, "content": {"raw": "DART also had the same issue and [adopted the workaround of using the environment variable](https://github.com/dartsim/dart/pull/1095), which I believe sdformat already does. One possible solution I can think of now is searching typical install locations (like [find_package](https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.8/command/find_package.html) does), which are platform dependent.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>DART also had the same issue and <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://github.com/dartsim/dart/pull/1095\" rel=\"nofollow\">adopted the workaround of using the environment variable</a>, which I believe sdformat already does. One possible solution I can think of now is searching typical install locations (like <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://cmake.org/cmake/help/v3.8/command/find_package.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">find_package</a> does), which are platform dependent.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-09-04T07:42:19.438728+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jeongseok Lee", "uuid": "{3907b560-aed7-43bd-bfa9-fd9873322291}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3907b560-aed7-43bd-bfa9-fd9873322291%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3907b560-aed7-43bd-bfa9-fd9873322291%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/242819b368397b2b4cddf273b2ba9bf8d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsJL-0.png"}}, "nickname": "jlee02", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:e3fbdece-a1d8-4fb6-a9f1-236ecb09bd9d"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 47603014}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/198/comments/47615832.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat/issues/198#comment-47615832"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat/issues/198.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 198, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/sdformat.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/sdformat"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}ts=1606789"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "sdformat", "full_name": "osrf/sdformat", "uuid": "{b6d52f9f-b070-41c0-807c-94af07ea375b}"}, "title": "sdformat install not relocatable: sdf::findFile searches original install location"}, "content": {"raw": "Yes, SDF already checks the `SDF_PATH` environment variable:\n\n* #!/osrf/sdformat/src/5eac19ab542539b1f0de63905d45a225e54651bc/src/SDF.cc#lines-105:120\n\nbut it does take an extra step to set that.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Yes, SDF already checks the <code>SDF_PATH</code> environment variable:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#!/osrf/sdformat/src/5eac19ab542539b1f0de63905d45a225e54651bc/src/SDF.cc#lines-105:120\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#!/osrf/sdformat/src/5eac19ab542539b1f0de63905d45a225e54651bc/src/SDF.cc#lines-105:120</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>but it does take an extra step to set that.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-09-04T18:11:17.741734+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15